snippet.title: Johnny Depp OFFICIALLY Sentenced To 2 Years In Prison - Amber Heard Wins…
snippet.description:
It is official, Johnny Depp has officially been sentenced to 2 years in prison for his crimes against Amber Heard. The two-year sentence will be served concurrently with the four prior months that he was sentenced to stay in rehab. Johnny is currently appealing his divorce settlement and an additional $100 million dollar judgment after he illegally smuggled the couple's dogs into Australia where he broke one of their quarantine laws by not having them properly vetted before entering the country. He also illegally failed to declare the two pets on customs forms when flying back into America. His defense argued that if they were listed on those forms, then they would have ended up dead due to something called "Animal Import Regulations".
